{"tid":2008654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華春瑩：中国不會成為伊拉克","createTime":"2020-05-09T07:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T04:58:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":157,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"347fe64f3a12c64f82ec04a0460cb1d6dcbdf4c7","tid":2008654,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0509/U656P22T1D824777F1DT20200509144525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F0509%2FU656P22T1D824777F1DT20200509144525.jpg&h=a7e8849f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月9日，中國外交部發言人華春瑩在推特上發了簡短有力的一句話：&ldquo;中國不會成為伊拉克&rdquo;(China won't be Iraq)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2020/0509/U656P22DT20200509144400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2020%2F0509%2FU656P22DT20200509144400.jpg&h=1ae4fb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推特配圖是美國有線電視新聞網(CNN)5日的報道截圖。當時的節目正在討論美國總統特朗普及其政府不惜余力地硬找所謂的&ldquo;證據&rdquo;，甚至施壓美國情報機構得出相關結論，以支持其&ldquo;實驗室泄露新冠病毒&rdquo;的陰謀論。<br />\n<br />\n　　時事評論家法里德&middot;紮卡里亞在接受采訪時直言，&ldquo;這讓我想起了伊拉克戰爭的開端。現在，你能看到白宮和國務院的某些官員在迫使和施壓情報機構得出一個結論，而情報機關明顯還沒準備好或永遠都不會得出這樣的結論。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;因為證據很不明確或者這根本不是正確答案。特朗普和蓬佩奧正試圖施壓情報機構說出，我們掌握某種關於中國的確鑿證據。正是因為這種政治化的情報導致了(美國發起)伊拉克戰爭的錯誤。我們正在看到歷史重演。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　在華春瑩這條推特的評論區，有人留言道：&ldquo;我們美國公民是無辜的，我們與他們無關。他們在殺死我們。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2020/0509/U656P22DT20200509144429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2020%2F0509%2FU656P22DT20200509144429.jpg&h=2b5dc828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0509/824777.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"28152280cb25011d9ebd534dfa56c1fc226322ea","tid":2008654,"uid":237562,"like":161,"dislike":1,"score":160,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"敍利亞啫"},{"pid":"af1ae1fe565d678f94206c785c6bc7a22e2c84a5","tid":2008654,"uid":264245,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"燈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe66cbdb3fc44e9030ec20d06afd40c4f9af651","tid":2008654,"uid":202340,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"伊拉克外交部幾時回應"},{"pid":"2f2f5a1e332cb94cdb51107cde9462c0d73abff6","tid":2008654,"uid":205469,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"會變蘇聯"},{"pid":"659617de7dd0dd0b6aa8c42e4d3ab8e8dca6d895","tid":2008654,"uid":31215,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"衰撚過伊拉克"},{"pid":"ba03754f822ac6b86209641b3685892c891d3ff2","tid":2008654,"uid":275903,"like":167,"dislike":1,"score":166,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"家陣伊拉克好失禮你呀<br />\n呢啲就直接翻譯十七國語文向中東做文宣"},{"pid":"dac9d4f62b89e422dd2ec7919b45fc41e2d52637","tid":2008654,"uid":8880,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"因為伊拉克都冇試過百國聯軍"},{"pid":"214a5bf823926bac6e6551f25e102a120357726c","tid":2008654,"uid":4917,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"變埃塞俄比亞"},{"pid":"892b6ba55788b730913d5fdd0fc17c50ce181da7","tid":2008654,"uid":226739,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ba03754f822ac6b86209641b3685892c891d3ff2","tid":2008654,"uid":275903,"like":167,"dislike":1,"score":166,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"家陣伊拉克好失禮你呀<br />\n呢啲就直接翻譯十七國語文向中東做文宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"Pin 呢個"},{"pid":"a7c0e68a234c14bfd6b33acc6d2e85126a2afe0e","tid":2008654,"uid":155095,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"變1911年嘅大清"},{"pid":"2d46a9df3343241fe46643502c23d52ffa59237f","tid":2008654,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba03754f822ac6b86209641b