008654,"uid":315761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"因為支那衰過伊拉克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfbc88e84096cd861f04e86cd43e9d5e84a4587","tid":2008654,"uid":6316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"又歧視人"},{"pid":"ccce7bced5fed111445b44a783b6c75f330f0851","tid":2008654,"uid":267730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"2019-07-24<br />\n<br />\n外交部发言人华春莹主持当日的例行记者会發言:<br />\n大家很清楚，我昨天在这里也提到，现在的美国国务卿、昔日美国最大的情报机构负责人蓬佩奥先生在今年4月的一场公开演讲上公然宣称，&ldquo;我们撒谎、我们欺骗、我们偷窃，这是美国不断探索前进的荣耀&rdquo;。但中国不一样。我们一不偷<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（美國知識產權呢？）</span></span>、二不抢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（南海d礁唔係搶，你做乜幾千年來唔填海今日先填？）</span></span>、三不撒谎<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同湖北閪武漢狗大聲講多次</span></span>。我们完全是靠自己的智慧和汗水<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做賊做雞都要血與汗既</span></span>取得了今天的骄人成就。如果说中国在打一场战争，那打的就是捍卫自身正当权益<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（利益咪抗疫每一個支那豬平均分30蚊俾佢，然後搵一個東北老坑寫文章吹噓&ldquo;黨每月俾千幾蚊我，令我過著蜜一樣甜既生活&rdquo;）</span></span>的正义战争。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">華春螢＝李桂華，可樂樽加洗衣粉吹成手榴彈果種撚狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"abd5377309cf1c21e2af0a34728a051a07eff9b1","tid":2008654,"uid":267730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1783285b5c11c17aeeafa0e6648fa8c6ba90c0fe","tid":2008654,"uid":304769,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"叫燒山講一次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"你放心今晚佢實講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc6f2608d7731353b3720f87176dbf0c156a74d","tid":2008654,"uid":268591,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:57:29.000Z","msg":"人地係真係死左好多人呀，你估真係數字咩。<br />\n對中國既忿怒巳經係全世界性的，仲係講呢啲廢話。"},{"pid":"5fcf84e6fdf63526c08062f785be849070b0d740","tid":2008654,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"中國人 ： sir this way"},{"pid":"dd060f735d7b079d6fef95518d4e8cc1b8c25d56","tid":2008654,"uid":266342,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"其實應該立法，禁止支那和其有關人等宣揚及使用twitter，facebook，youtube<br />\n而且另外世界各國亦都要立例禁止登入Weibo丶wechat等<br />\n<br />\n由得佢自己自成一個同世界斷絕任何關係"},{"pid":"7b1427a28757fb1b03409804a106563513db3e3f","tid":2008654,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"變成納粹德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd842fcc2437cd3a209e9d19d233e4498099ac9","tid":2008654,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1427a28757fb1b03409804a106563513db3e3f","tid":2008654,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"變成納粹德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"因為依家都差唔多係"},{"pid":"4a601938836bedc65ed8dcd79630cd0bdb58139a","tid":2008654,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dd842fcc2437cd3a209e9d19d233e4498099ac9","tid":2008654,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1427a28757fb1b03409804a106563513db3e3f","tid":2008654,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"變成納粹德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"因為依家都差唔多係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"似意粉多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c164ee94157ab4e443070931879d8e72c0da99","tid":2008654,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac9d4f62b89e422dd2ec7919b45fc41e2d52637","tid":2008654,"uid":8880,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"因為伊拉克都冇試過百國聯軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1198ad431295cb54e173235a92d5a2d21f5851b","tid":2008654,"uid":194130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"347fe64f3a12c64f82ec04a0460cb1d6dcbdf4c7","tid":2008654,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0509/U656P22T1D824777F1DT20200509144525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F0509%2FU656P22T1D824777F1DT20200509144525.jpg&h=a7e8849f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月9日，中國外交部發言人華春瑩在推特上發了簡短有力的一句話：&ldquo;中國不會成為伊拉克&rdquo;(China won't be Iraq)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2020/0509/U656P22DT20200509144400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2020%2F0509%2FU656P22DT20200509144400.jpg&h=1ae4fb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推特配圖是美國有線電視新聞網(CNN)5日的報道截圖。當時的節目正在討論美國總統特朗普及其政府不惜余力地硬找所謂的&ldquo;證據&rdquo;，甚至施壓美國情報機構得出相關結論，以支持其&ldquo;實驗室泄露新冠病毒&rdquo;的陰謀論。<br />\n<br />\n　　時事評論家法里德&middot;紮卡里亞在接受采訪時直言，&ldquo;這讓我想起了伊拉克戰爭的開端。現在，你能看到白宮和國務院的某些官員在迫使和施壓情報機構得出一個結論，而情報機關明顯還沒準備好或永遠都不會得出這樣的結論。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;因為證據很不明確或者這根本不是正確答案。特朗普和蓬佩奧正試圖施壓情報機構說出，我們掌握某種關於中國的確鑿證據。正是因為這種政治化的情報導致了(美國發起)伊拉克戰爭的錯誤。我們正在看到歷史重演。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　在華春瑩這條推特的評論區，有人留言道：&ldquo;我們美國公民是無辜的，我們與他們無關。他們在殺死我們。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2020/0509/U656P22DT20200509144429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2020%2F0509%2FU656P22DT20200509144429.jpg&h=2b5dc828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0509/824777.shtml</code></pre>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"中国不會成為伊拉克<br />\n伊拉克-&gt;最後搵唔到證據-&gt;無辜受害者<br />\n中国-&gt;證據確鑿-&gt;罪有應得死牚到底<br />\n點睇都唔一樣"},{"pid":"0099aa5b3d6e678a92389c4ebc710ab35041558a","tid":2008654,"uid":159307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"變戈壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504e2896ea6a3627c9726284ad03d6eeadd1e453","tid":2008654,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"今次仲唔仆街<br />\n肯定衰撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2901cce4181f59bcd7a8b8fb966d9ba25755d866","tid":2008654,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"Self-fulfilling prophecy <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd52b6763d98e182b75c227bf806cfcc62ff2244","tid":2008654,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"會變俄屬支那/美屬支那/台屬支那/法屬支那/英屬支那，世界免費共享支那十四億奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7574005669ec6d44c734c1e4de41294a81fcb462","tid":2008654,"uid":301100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c0e68a234c14bfd6b33acc6d2e85126a2afe0e","tid":2008654,"uid":155095,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"變1911年嘅大清"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"偉大復興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ece6f7c6f6f1d58ba0cf85775a3a2853725d5a","tid":2008654,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05